  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003ENon-exempt, full-time employees earn PTO through an accrual system based on years of service. PTO balances cap at 120 hours, with rollover allowed up to that limit. Requests must be approved in advance and scheduled around business needs. This system ensures equitable time-off benefits for hourly employees while maintaining operational coverage.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
